story.storyDescription: Chastity isn't as chaste as you think she is.
story.title: Chastity

messages.text: U R DEAD BITCH!!!!
Chastity?
U know damn well its me.
Sorry, didn’t know you had a phone.
Eat shit.
What? Lots of poor people don’t have phones.
Stay AWAY from him!
No idea what U mean.
Like hell.
Christ. Is this about Adam?
Saw u w/ him in study hall.
So? He’s assigned to my table.
No. SAW you WITH him!
Don’t know what U think U saw.
I KNOW what I saw.
Getting bored with this. Nothing happened.
I saw his hand on UR leg!
Oh that. Not sure how thats my fault. : p
U R such a BITCH!
Better than being a prude.
WHAT?!
Yeah. Adam told me all about U.
Bullshit.
All talk and no action. He called U a tease with daddy issues.
UR lying.
We both know that’s not true. Unless Adam is lying.. b/c he claims he calls U that all the time. ☺
Fuck U. Im warning U 2 stay away.
Why should I?
BECAUE I LOVE HIM!
Sorry 4 U then. Thats a 1 way street.
They have those where U live, don’t they? Or R those just dead ends. Hard to tell from all the way up here.
U think having $ means U get everything U want?
No.
I KNOW it does. And having nothing means U get nothing.
Why R U doing this?  U KNOW he means nothing to U.
He’s cute. : )
And poor. Like me.
Not like U. No 1 does poor quite like U Chastity. U R the best at it.
Fuck U! He’s not part of UR world. U people will never accept him. Ur lawyer daddy will never let him within a mile of ur palace, PRINCESS!
Maybe not. But if daddy isn’t here.. who’s 2 say?
U R a whore.
Maybe.. good thing Adam will be here soon.
LIAR!
Believe what U want.
Why would he go there?
Um, lets see. Maybe b/c his ex is a frigid bitch who doesn’t know what guys want.
He’s not my EX. We’re still 2gether.
Not according 2 him.
UR a fool if u believe that.
Know soon enough. My parents will b gone and Adam will b here. And then..
He won’t. Not if u were the last bitch on earth.
We’ll see. Ask him at school Monday. Then look in his eyes and see 4 yourself.
And then what? U throw him away like u did 2 Will?
Ah.. there it is.
What?
All the trailer trash blame me for Will.. but Will had issues.
B/c of U. U used him and dumped him like a piece of trash.
He is trash. Like U.
Oops. Sorry, he WAS trash.
U R EVIL. Will was a tragedy.. U broke his heart.. all b/c U felt like slumming it 4 a week.
I can’t be responsible 4 every guy who falls 4 me.
And what about the brother who found him? Fifteen years old and he will never b the same.
Martin?
MORGAN! U heartless piece of shit!
Poor Morgan.
Get it? Poor. B/c he lives near u in that parking lot.
Yes he does. And b/c of u he’s gonna grow up an only child.
Still don’t see how Will is my fault.
You got in his head and made him think you actually liked him b4 you flung him to the side of the road. And now he’s gone.
What can I say? It WAS a fling.
Not 4 him!!
If it makes u feel better.. I really didn’t enjoy it all that much.  = (
Swear to God Im coming there 2 beat the shit out of u.
Good luck getting in. Said it yourself. It’s a palace, not a double wide.
U think a gate and a locked door will keep me out?
Trust me. Better than u have tried.
Rich fucks like u don’t understand that people like me have nothing to lose.
Everyone has something to lose. Like ur virginity.
We’ll see.
Snore. Gotta go and get ready for my visitor.
I’ll give u 1 last chance 2 stay away from Adam.
And I’ll give u some free advice since its all u can afford.. maybe next time don’t take ur name so literally if u want to keep a guy, Chastity.
Changed my mind.
About?
I’m not gonna beat u, I’m gonna kill u.
Frightening. But hold that thought, someone’s at the door. Now who could it b?
UR lying.
He certainly looks like Adam. But u said he would never come here.
Don’t believe Uu
Nope. I was right. Its him. He says to tell you hi.
Like I said U R dead.
Sounds great.
I’m not kidding.
Sorry.. we gotta go. I’d keep the security cameras rolling 4 u but I don’t think daddy would approve.
That’s all we wanted to hear.
We?
Adam?
Yeah, I’m here.
Was she telling the truth?
Yep. She’s alone. No one else is here.
And Evie?
Oddly.. she looks even more smug without front teeth.. but there’s still plenty of fight in her.
Good.
Is Morgan with u?
Yep.
Cool. Come on up. The door is open.
